{"id":683033,"date":"2023-12-29T16:01:08","date_gmt":"2023-12-29T10:31:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=683033"},"modified":"2025-03-19T15:53:16","modified_gmt":"2025-03-19T10:23:16","slug":"why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree","title":{"rendered":"Top reasons why MA is a versatile degree\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>In the vast academic playground, a Master of Arts (MA) degree reigns supreme, showcasing its versatility like a chameleon with a colorful palette. In other words, the endless <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/why-pursue-online-ma-from-sikkim-manipal-university#:~:text=Versatile%20skill%20set%3A%20Online%20education,today's%20rapidly%20changing%20work%20environment.\">benefits of a versatile Master of Arts education <\/a>act as a backstage pass to various lucrative career stages.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A Master of Arts (MA) degree program helps transform a graduate into an energetic professional who can thrive in the rapidly changing work environment in an Artificial Intelligence (AI) era. This 2-year postgraduate program is no less than a catalyst for versatility, shaping individuals into well-rounded contributors to society with a profound understanding of their chosen field.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, buckle up as we take you through a landscape for a better understanding of the <strong>versatility of a Master of Arts degree.<\/strong> In the same post, we will also guide you about the best university to pursue an online MA degree course, so stay tuned!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-why-pursue-an-online-ma-degree\"><strong>Why pursue an online MA degree?\u00a0<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The traditional way of pursuing a Master of Arts (MA) course is through a campus program. But it is time you change to go on an educational journey and get a passport to a global learning community. In short, it is time to choose to pursue an online MA program instead of a traditional campus program. Pursuing an online MA degree course is not just about flexibility but much more than that.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentioned below are the key <strong>advantages of pursuing an MA for versatility <\/strong>online:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Wide range of specializations to choose from: <\/strong>The prime <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/why-pursue-online-ma-from-sikkim-manipal-university\"><strong>advantage of pursuing an online MA program<\/strong><\/a> is that it allows you to choose your favorite subjects like English, Political Science, and Sociology. So, in short, choices are ample in terms of specializations for anyone keen to pursue a Master of Arts degree program.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Gain versatile skill set: <\/strong>Communication skills, time management, digital literacy, adaptability, and self-discipline are some of the key skills gained by an online MA graduate after finishing the course.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Explore a wide range of jobs: <\/strong>With an online MA degree in hand, one can grab exciting job roles in healthcare administration, psychology, teaching, writing, business, and management after finishing your MA course online.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Career advancement: <\/strong>Not to forget that with an online MA degree, you can undoubtedly increase your career prospects. It is because these courses are designed to allow you flexibility and impart both theoretical and practical knowledge that can be used in today&#8217;s progressive work environments.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Easy to switch careers: <\/strong>The wide range of online Master of Arts (MA) programs offered at universities like the best universities like Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) offer you a brilliant scope to explore new fields. One of the key skills taught to online MA students is adaptability, and this helps them easily switch to new careers.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-skills-you-get-after-completing-an-ma-degree\"><strong>Skills you get after completing an MA degree\u00a0<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from the main advantage of learning while retaining your current employment, the versatile skill set one acquires with an online MA degree makes it a viable option for many. This is an apt PG program that will prepare you to climb higher on the career ladder.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let us elaborate a bit by listing out the primary skills you get after completing an MA degree:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Research skills: <\/strong>No matter which subject you choose for an MA degree program, research is an integral part of this course. During this course, an individual harnesses refined research skills that can go a long way in all types of careers.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Effective communication: <\/strong>You learn to convey your ideas with clarity and conviction based on the effective written and verbal communication skills gained with an MA degree program.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Problem-solving: <\/strong>As one proceeds to specialize in a particular subject through a Master of Arts (MA) course, one learns to tackle various challenges and problems systematically and analytically. This enhances the problem-solving skills of an individual.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Critical thinking: <\/strong>A Master of Arts (MA) degree program also hones a person&#8217;s critical thinking. This leads them to evaluate arguments with better information analyses to make informed decisions in their respective careers.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-top-ma-degrees-to-pursue\"><strong>Top MA degrees to pursue<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No doubt, a Master of Arts (MA) course stands as a gateway to specialized knowledge, offering you the golden opportunity for intellectual enrichment in your chosen subject. The options are endless, and one might get confused about picking the right one, so we thought of sharing details about 7 top MA courses for your reference:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>MA in English: <\/strong>Master of Arts (MA) in English is one of the most preferred choices for those keen to pursue higher education. It is a 2-year course designed to enable a person to explore the various literary genres and critical approaches. Some of the primary skills gained during an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-arts-english#:~:text=The%20online%20MA%20in%20English%20curriculum%20offered%20by%20Sikkim%20Manipal,refer%20to%20the%20program%20brochure.\"><strong>online MA in English course from Sikkim Manipal University through the Online Manipal platform<\/strong><\/a> are communication and research skills, critical thinking skills, and writing skills.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Listed below are the top 5 job opportunities open for MA in English graduates:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Content Writer<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Journalist\/ Reporter<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Human Resource Manager<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Public Relation Manager<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Teacher\/ Professor<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>MA in Sociology: <\/strong>This 2-year PG course aims to equip students with research methodologies, and advanced theoretical frameworks relevant for society. The main skills gained during an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/np\/master-of-arts-sociology\"><strong>online MA in Sociology course<\/strong><\/a> are understanding social policies and human behavior, research and analytical skills, and critical thinking skills.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a look at the top 5 career opportunities after an MA in Sociology:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Sociologist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Social Worker<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Marriage Counsellor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Community Organizer<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Human Research Specialist<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>MA in Political Science: <\/strong>If the political area excites you, then go for an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/SMU-MA-Political-Science-Domestic-Brochure.pdf\">online MA in Political Science from Sikkim Manipal University<\/a><strong>. <\/strong>This PG course will equip you to understand the complex political scenario around the world so that you can contribute to policy discussions for the benefit of all.\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Listed below are the top 5 career prospects after an MA in Political Science:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Political consultant<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Diplomat<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Policy Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Policy Campaign Strategist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>International Relation Specialist<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>MA in Journalism: <\/strong>Designed to teach an individual the vivid aspects of journalism, such as reporting, writing, and storytelling, an MA in Journalism degree course acts as a launch pad for several exciting careers in the media industry. During the course, students get hands-on experience through internships and newsroom simulations.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>The list below reveals the best 5 career opportunities for an MA in Journalism graduates:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Journalist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Editor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Public Relations Manager\/ Event Manager<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Digital Media Strategist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Communication Specialist<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"5\">\n<li><strong>MA in Psychology: <\/strong>If it is the human psyche that entices you, then the best option for you is to pursue an MA in Psychology from a reputed university. This course can serve as a stepping stone for one who wants to understand psychological theories and methodologies. During the course, students get to engage not just in the coursework but also in research and practical training.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Listed below are the top 5 career options after an MA in Psychology:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Clinical Psychologist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Child Psychologist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Forensic Psychologist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Academician<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Human Resource Manager<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"6\">\n<li><strong>MA in History: <\/strong>The main focus of an MA in History degree program is to equip a student with historiography, critical interpretation of historical sources, and archival research. This 2-year postgraduate program offers a deep level of understanding of the complexities of the past.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><\/strong>Mentioned below are the top 5 job opportunities after an MA in History:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Historian<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Documentary Filmmaker<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Archivist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educator<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Curator<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"7\">\n<li><strong>MA in Economics: <\/strong>The<strong> <\/strong>Master of Arts (MA) in Economics is about the advanced study of economic theories and policies. The main subjects taught in an MA in Economics are macroeconomics, microeconomics, and economic analysis. On completion of this 2-year PG course, students become skilled in researching, data analyzing, and critical thinking.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentioned below are the top 5 career options open for an MA in Economics graduate:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Economist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>International Trade Specialist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Professor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Financial Analyst<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-why-choose-an-online-ma-from-smu\"><strong>Why choose an online MA from SMU<\/strong>\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By now, we assume you must have received plenty of answers about why MA is an adaptable degree choice. So, let us further explain where and how to pursue it. In today&#8217;s busy lifestyle, why take the pain of commuting to the campus daily to pursue a Master of Arts course when you can easily opt for an online MA from Sikkim Manipal University through the Online Platform?\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Listed below are the top reasons for which we recommend you to pursue an online MA course from Sikkim Manipal University (SMU):<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>NAAC A+ accreditation: <\/strong>The prime reason for anyone to enroll in an online Master of Arts course from Sikkim Manipal University is its recognition and accreditation. The university is recognized by UGC and has an NAAC A+ accreditation, hence all the degrees rewarded are globally accepted by employers in all industries.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>Global access: <\/strong>Online MA courses from Sikkim Manipal University can be pursued by anyone within the country and outside. Students from Nepal, UAE, Bhutan, and other neighboring countries prefer pursuing an online MA from this university through the Online Manipal platform.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>Industry-relevant curriculum: <\/strong>Another benefit a student can reap by enrolling in an online MA course from Sikkim Manipal University is acquiring skills relevant to excelling in particular industries. This is because the university offers MA courses with a curriculum that syncs with the current world scenario.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>Robust Manipal alumni brand: <\/strong>Getting associated with the prestigious Manipal alumni brand is a dream for many, and the best way to make it a reality is by enrolling in an online MA degree course. You get to network with expert professionals from all fields across the globe and learn from their experience by being a part of the Manipal brand.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"5\">\n<li><strong>Affordable fee: <\/strong>Many refrain from pursuing higher education due to the expensive fee structure. However, there is nothing to worry about regarding finances if you pursue an online MA from Sikkim Manipal University. It is because Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) offers such courses at pocket-friendly fees with a no-cost EMI flexible payment system.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-conclusion\"><strong>Conclusion\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The flexibility and versatility of an MA degree is such that it has emerged as the most popular postgraduate program not just in India but abroad too. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-arts\">Pursuing an online MA course<\/a> from an established university like Sikkim Manipal University through the Online Manipal platform means enjoying much flexibility to accommodate your other professional and personal commitments with a perfect balance. Get access to online lectures and interactive sessions during the course and placement assistance after the course from expert faculty who have a rich experience in their respective industries. All this can be within your reach at an affordable fee for Sikkim Manipal University&#8217;s online MA courses.\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In the vast academic playground, a Master of Arts (MA) degree reigns supreme, showcasing its versatility like a chameleon with a colorful palette. In other words, the endless benefits of a versatile Master of Arts education act as a backstage pass to various lucrative career stages.\u00a0 A Master of Arts (MA) degree program helps transform [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":19,"featured_media":682276,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[218],"tags":[19,230,220],"class_list":["post-683033","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-arts","tag-online-degree","tag-online-ma","tag-sikkim-manipal-university"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>Top reasons why MA is a versatile degree\u00a0 - Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"What makes an online MA from Sikkim Manipal University a versatile degree? Top benefits of pursuing an MA program, Skills you get after an MA degree.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/683033\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Top reasons why MA is a versatile degree\u00a0 - Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"What makes an online MA from Sikkim Manipal University a versatile degree? Top benefits of pursuing an MA program, Skills you get after an MA degree.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2023-12-29T10:31:08+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2025-03-19T10:23:16+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/Why-should-you-pursue-an-online-MA-from-SMU@2x-100.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1412\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"790\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Editorial Team\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:label1\" content=\"Written by\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data1\" content=\"Editorial Team\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:label2\" content=\"Estimated reading time\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data2\" content=\"9 minutes\" \/>\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\" class=\"yoast-schema-graph\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree\",\"name\":\"Top reasons why MA is a versatile degree\u00a0 - Online Manipal\",\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/#website\"},\"primaryImageOfPage\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree#primaryimage\"},\"image\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree#primaryimage\"},\"thumbnailUrl\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2023\\\/11\\\/Why-should-you-pursue-an-online-MA-from-SMU@2x-100.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2023-12-29T10:31:08+00:00\",\"dateModified\":\"2025-03-19T10:23:16+00:00\",\"description\":\"What makes an online MA from Sikkim Manipal University a versatile degree? Top benefits of pursuing an MA program, Skills you get after an MA degree.\",\"breadcrumb\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree#breadcrumb\"},\"inLanguage\":\"en-GB\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"ReadAction\",\"target\":[\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree\"]}]},{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"inLanguage\":\"en-GB\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree#primaryimage\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2023\\\/11\\\/Why-should-you-pursue-an-online-MA-from-SMU@2x-100.jpg\",\"contentUrl\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2023\\\/11\\\/Why-should-you-pursue-an-online-MA-from-SMU@2x-100.jpg\",\"width\":1412,\"height\":790,\"caption\":\"Online MA is a versatile degree\"},{\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/why-online-ma-is-a-versatile-degree#breadcrumb\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Top reasons why MA is a versatile degree\u00a0\"}]},{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/#website\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/\",\"name\":\"Online Manipal\",\"description\":\"Online Manipal\",\"publisher\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/#organization\"},\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":{\"@type\":\"PropertyValueSpecification\",\"valueRequired\":true,\"valueName\":\"search_term_string\"}}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-G